{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_db07e4b3daf046ffb2a2618a","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" standalone=\"yes\"?>\n2\t<addon id=\"plugin.video.netflix\" name=\"Netflix\" version=\"1.23.5+matrix.1\" provider-name=\"libdev, jojo, asciidisco, caphm, castagnait\">\n3\t  <requires>\n4\t    <import addon=\"xbmc.python\" version=\"3.0.0\"/>\n5\t    <import addon=\"script.module.addon.signals\" version=\"0.0.6+matrix.1\"/>\n6\t    <import addon=\"script.module.inputstreamhelper\" version=\"0.5.0+matrix.1\"/>\n7\t    <import addon=\"script.module.pycryptodome\" version=\"3.4.3\"/>\n8\t    <import addon=\"script.module.requests\"/>\n9\t    <import addon=\"script.module.myconnpy\" version=\"8.0.18+matrix.1\"/> <!--MySQL Connector/Python-->\n10\t  </requires>\n11\t  <extension point=\"xbmc.python.pluginsource\" library=\"addon.py\">\n12\t    <provides>video</provides>\n13\t  </extension>\n14\t  <extension point=\"xbmc.service\" library=\"service.py\"/>\n15\t  <extension point=\"xbmc.addon.metadata\">\n16\t    <reuselanguageinvoker>true</reuselanguageinvoker>\n17\t    <summary lang=\"cs_CZ\">Netflix</summary>\n18\t    <description lang=\"cs_CZ\">Plugin pro sledování filmů, seriálů online z Netflixu</description>\n19\t    <disclaimer lang=\"cs_CZ\">Použití tohoto doplňku nemusí být ve vaší zemi pobytu legální - před instalací dbejte na vaše zákony.</disclaimer>\n20\t    <summary lang=\"de_DE\">Netflix</summary>\n21\t    <description lang=\"de_DE\">Addon für Netflix VOD-Dienste</description>\n22\t    <disclaimer lang=\"de_DE\">Möglicherweise ist die Verwendung dieses Addons in Ihrem Land illegal, Sie sollten dies unbedingt vor der Installation überprüfen.</disclaimer>\n23\t    <summary lang=\"en_GB\">Netflix</summary>\n24\t    <description lang=\"en_GB\">Netflix VOD Services Add-on</description>\n25\t    <disclaimer lang=\"en_GB\">The use of this add-on may not be legal in your country of residence - please check with your local laws before installing.</disclaimer>\n26\t    <summary lang=\"el_GR\">Νέτφλιξ</summary>\n27\t    <description lang=\"el_GR\">Πρόσθετο υπηρεσιών κατά παραγγελία του Νέτφλιξ</description>\n28\t    <disclaimer lang=\"el_GR\">Η χρήση αυτού του προσθέτου μπορεί να μην είναι νόμιμη στην χώρα που κατοικείτε - παρακαλώ ελέγξτε τους τοπικούς νόμους πριν την εγκατάσταση.</disclaimer>\n29\t    <summary lang=\"nl_NL\">Netflix</summary>\n30\t    <description lang=\"nl_NL\">Bekijk Netflix films en tvprogramma's in Kodi.</description>\n31\t    <disclaimer lang=\"nl_NL\">Sommige delen van deze add-on zijn mogelijk onwettig in jouw land - raadpleeg de lokale wetgeving alvorens deze add-on te installeren.</disclaimer>\n32\t    <summary lang=\"ja_JP\">Netflix</summary>\n33\t    <description lang=\"ja_JP\">Netflix VOD サービスアドオン</description>\n34\t    <disclaimer lang=\"ja_JP\">一部の国では、このアドオンを使用するのが不法でありますので、設置する前に必ず関連法律を確認してください</disclaimer>\n35\t    <summary lang=\"ko_KR\">Netflix</summary>\n36\t    <description lang=\"ko_KR\">Netflix VOD 서비스애드온</description>\n37\t    <disclaimer lang=\"ko_KR\">일부 국가에서는 이 애드온을 사용하는 것이 불법일 수도 있으니, 설치하기전 관련 법을 확인하기 바랍니다.</disclaimer>\n38\t    <description lang=\"it_IT\">Netflix Add-on servizi VOD</description>\n39\t    <disclaimer lang=\"it_IT\">L'utilizzo di questo add-on potrebbe non essere legale nel vostro paese di residenza - si prega di verificare le leggi in vigore prima dell'installazione.</disclaimer>\n40\t    <summary lang=\"es_ES\">Netflix</summary>\n41\t    <description lang=\"es_ES\">Complemento para los Servicios VOD de Netflix</description>\n42\t    <disclaimer lang=\"es_ES\">El uso de este complemento puede no ser legal en su país de residencia - Por favor, consulte las leyes locales antes de instalarlo.</disclaimer>\n43\t    <summary lang=\"hu_HU\">Netflix</summary>\n44\t    <description lang=\"hu_HU\">Netflix VOD kiegészítő a Kodihoz</description>\n45\t    <disclaimer lang=\"hu_HU\">Előfordulhat, hogy a kiegészítő használata nem törvényes az Ön országában - telepítés előtt tájékozódjon a helyi törvényekről</disclaimer>\n46\t    <summary lang=\"pt_BR\">Netflix</summary>\n47\t    <description lang=\"pt_BR\">Add-on para os serviços VOD do Netflix</description>\n48\t    <disclaimer lang=\"pt_BR\">O uso deste addon pode não ser legal no seu país de residência - por favor, verifique as suas leis locais antes de instalar.</disclaimer>\n49\t    <summary lang=\"tr_TR\">Netflix</summary>\n50\t    <description lang=\"tr_TR\">Netflix VOD Hizmetleri Eklentisi</description>\n51\t    <disclaimer lang=\"tr_TR\">Bu eklentinin bazı bölümleri ikamet ettiğiniz ülkede yasal olmayabilir - lütfen yüklemeden önce yerel yasalarınıza bakın.</disclaimer>\n52\t    <summary lang=\"ro_RO\">Netflix</summary>\n53\t    <description lang=\"ro_RO\">Add-on pentru servicii video la cerere Netflix</description>\n54\t    <disclaimer lang=\"ro_RO\">Utilizarea acestui add-on ar putea fi ilegală în țara în care locuiți - vă rugăm să verificați legile locale înainte de instalare.</disclaimer>\n55\t    <summary lang=\"sv_SE\">Netflix</summary>\n56\t    <description lang=\"sv_SE\">Netflix VOD Service-tillägg</description>\n57\t    <disclaimer lang=\"sv_SE\">Användandet av detta tillägg kanske inte är lagligt i ditt hemland - kontrollera med dina lokala lagar innan du installerar.</disclaimer>\n58\t    <summary lang=\"zh_CN\">Netflix</summary>\n59\t    <description lang=\"zh_CN\">Netflix VOD服务附加组件</description>\n60\t    <disclaimer lang=\"zh_CN\">此附加组件在您的居住国可能不合法-请在安装前与您当地的法律核对。</disclaimer>\n61\t    <summary lang=\"fr_FR\">Netflix</summary>\n62\t    <description lang=\"fr_FR\">Extension Netflix SVoD</description>\n63\t    <disclaimer lang=\"fr_FR\">L'utilisation de cette extension n'est peut-être pas légale dans votre pays de résidence - renseignez-vous avant de l'installer</disclaimer>\n64\t    <summary lang=\"pl_PL\">Netflix</summary>\n65\t    <description lang=\"pl_PL\">Wtyczka dla usług VOD serwisu Netflix</d